ate type="date" label="Date" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true" display="localdateshort" UTC="true">20130321T18:00:00</Date><Author type="string" label="Author's Name" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Marc Stevens</Author><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Height=""><![CDATA[<p>Over the last year, a considerable amount of work has been done at BYU-Idaho to foster and enhance transparent, two-way communication with employees throughout all levels of the university.&nbsp;</p>
<p>While the effort is ongoing, an important new initiative - "Join the Conversation: Be Informed. Be Heard." - has been designed to facilitate the process. New communication tools are being implemented all across the university, with the goal of making it easier than ever for employees to be part of the conversation.&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can learn more at www.byui.edu/join-the-conversation.</p>
